race.description: Ladbrokes Popular Srm Fillies & Mares Maiden Plate
race.comment: MISLIGHT (4) has had a few chances but looks to have found a very winnable maiden. She found the 1200m far too sharp first up off a short break, quickly getting to this track and trip last time when giving a good sight, beaten a head. Should be at peak fitness now. She rolls to the top and goes close. FEDORA (10) is knocking on the door, placing in her past couple including when just behind MISLIGHT last time out. She's open to further improvement and looks the danger again. SHARK PARK (8) was just fair fresh when in the market but should strip fitter for that and is very lightly raced. Respecting with the added fitness. DELA BELLA (1) was disappointing as favourite behind MISLIGHT last time but has to be respected off that support. HOLLER DASH (2) could stick on for a minor placing.
